Regulation Name(s): Calculator/Data Processing Module for Clinical Use
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): Blood glucose meters with data management capabilities
Polymap Wireless Polytel GMA Glucose Meter Accessory
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for InTouchTM-diabetes software accessory enabling data transmission and analysis of blood glucose meter readings for diabetes management
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for home use by adults to aid diabetes management through review and analysis of historical blood glucose results as an accessory to compatible blood glucose meters, not for treatment decision or substitute for professional judgment
